{"id":195207,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":22}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"428","ytitle":"","mtitle":"民谣抄","ftitle":"","authors":["王知四"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王知四　辑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主心脏毒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们身上看“三国”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油水压干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他去享福禄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注一)“看三国”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用计谋的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有钱会压人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人走头无门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年苦一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年不够还“债神”。(注一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注一)“债神”，放债的地主。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜苦来日夜忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴到粮食收到场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主大船装满舱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢下两麻袋，还说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“还未扣陈账”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同人家种田怎么了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦得二顿吃不饱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大的哭，小的哼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没良心的地主还叫做“小跑”。(注一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注一)做“小跑”，是做打杂等事情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小姐”出嫁“唔唔哇”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红木嫁妆赔到家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家姑娘要出门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马桶还是借人家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少奶奶“塔”得品品香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见到我们脸变样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捏着鼻子叫后退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕我们穷气沾到她衣裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同“老爷”长瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同“老爷”摸虾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜水流不到我嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜汤喝不到半口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在“老爷”家吃饭做白工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们出门我推送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一世还喊我大呆瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“死后棺材不知在那家。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出力出汗要吃饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老爷”“奶奶”都骂我吃得慢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢倒不慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不能我少吃一碗饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一○"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗腿子上门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要拿鸡蛋敬神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃得不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么过门。"}]}